<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Knowledge Approval Request</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic reset for email clients */
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; }
        table { border-spacing: 0; width: 100%; }
        td { padding: 0; }
        .container { width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border: 1px solid #eeeeee; }
        
        /* Header: Black background */
        .header { background-color: #000000; padding: 25px 20px; text-align: left; }
        .logo { max-height: 45px; display: block; border: 0; }
        
        .content { padding: 30px; background-color: #ffffff; }
        
        /* Article Info Table */
        .details-table { background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #dddddd; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .details-table td { padding: 5px 0; font-size: 14px; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; width: 120px; color: #555555; }
        
        /* Footer: Black background */
        .footer { background-color: #000000; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #ffffff; }
        .footer p { margin: 5px 0; opacity: 0.8; }
        
        /* Updated Button: Black background with white text */
        .button { 
            background-color: #000000; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            padding: 14px 30px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            display: inline-block; 
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid #333333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table role="presentation" class="container">
<tr>
    <td class="header" style="background-color: #000000; padding: 25px 20px;">
        <img src="https://andersonadvisors--octopus.sandbox.my.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015VG000007ubqT&oid=00DVG000006qsth&lastMod=1778079611000" 
             alt="Anderson Business Advisors" 
             style="max-height: 45px; display: block; border: 0; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); -webkit-filter: brightness(0) invert(1);">
    </td>
</tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="content">
                <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Hello {!User.FirstName},</h2>
                <p>A Knowledge Article has been submitted and is awaiting your review and approval.</p>
                
                <div class="details-table">
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label">Title:</td>
                            <td>{!Knowledge__kav.Title}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label">Article #:</td>
                            <td>{!Knowledge__kav.ArticleNumber}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label">Submitted By:</td>
                            <td>{!User.FirstName} {!User.LastName}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label">Comments:</td>
                            <td>{!ApprovalRequest.Comments}</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <p>Please review the article details and take the appropriate action via the button below.</p>
                
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                    <a href="{!$Label.Org_Lightning_Domain}/lightning/r/ProcessInstanceWorkitem/{!Workitem.ID}/view" class="button">Review & Approve Article</a>
                </p>
                
                <p>Thanks,<br><strong>The Anderson Team</strong></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="footer">
                <p>&copy; 2026 Anderson Business Advisors. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This is an automated internal approval notification.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>